text: The Mojo Jojo Series: How does Mojo stay so slim and trim? Well, it's not by eating vegetables. That's for humans. A descendant of carnivores, Mojo eats a lean diet of bison and water buffalo meat, which he obtains on his annual hunts with packs of gray wolves in the arctic. pic.twitter.com/F33kDr9Xmm
